channel.title: PI 317 - Project Soundwave 24/7 // Olldschool
channel.description:
[center][img]http://www.project-soundwave.com/img/title2/rslogo3.png[/img][/center]
[center]We are a new pvp/economy based server that is open for everyone! please visit our website for the client or download it at the bottom! This server is oldskool one, we did not added any costums or any weird things that does not exist in the real Rs.. Further i like to thank all the players that has been voting,
Come give us a visit and enjoy playing!
Atm we are only looking for moderators, so please if you wanna apply, give us a call or email us at: Dracel-inc@hotmail.com
Players: 26 registered already! Dont forget to vote every hour! Please enjoy!
[img]http://dauntlessmedia.net/wp-content/uploads/front-page/logo_recent-updates.png[/img]
